item.title: Dream March Moon
item.author: jsacosta1103@gmail.com (Jerad Acosta)
item.description: March 7th: She is off to New Zealand Experience: A snake for leaving a snake for lying A familiar adversary appeared in his young spiritual guide form along with his powerful master. A powerful and rightful lord among the spirits the only individual I have seen him respect and revered as unrivaled March 9th: Legolanded safe and clear of snakes Dream: Reaching for another young shell Drifting into a comfortable day dream
